The story revolves around this character named <br>
EON. Who is out to destroy this evil force that destroyed his village killing all his clansmen and father in the process. His mother died of mysterious causes five years prior to the attack. Now the way his father died was in a final confrontation with the force to end it all, but he was unsuccessful and finds out a Shocking fact about the force. Eon is about 8 when this happens. Also around the same time Eon's father (Jin'emon) friends Sanenori is attacked by the force and achieves and an evil power calle kaishaku that will destroy anyone who is not strong of heart and mind. Well Jin'emon comes to Sanenori in a dream and ask him to take care of his son eon. Sanenori finds him and starts training him to use of kaishaku. Also at this time eon's father's spirit is training his son in the way of a dragoon combat. Acombat sword technique that has been passed down through generations. The only memento of eon's father that he has is his sword which has the souls of his fallen clansmen in it and stained with the blood of his father. Eon is now about 22 and sets out on his journey to destroy the evil with his mentor Sanenori by his side to complete what has benn foretold in his blood since before he was born. On his journey he will meet allies that act like enemies and enemies that play mind tricks with him all the time. That is a little bit about my book. The rest of it is too long to just type and I don't want to go to all the details right now, cause there are a lot of plot twist that happens with each one of the minor characters. <br>
For now just tell me what you think of this.  <p>Tell them death is coming for them tonight<br>
<br>
